of proposed regulations on small entities whenever it is anticipated that any small entities may be adversely impacted.
Because it was anticipated that some small wood furniture manufacturers could be adversely impacted from implementation
of the proposed standards, a regulatory flexibility analysis was performed. A copy of the Economic Impact Regulatory
