Agency also seeks comment on whether a facility that is 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
initially determined to be subject to the rule should be 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
able subsequently to escape applicability, and if so, under 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
