<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Supelco seeks approval to manufacture individual pure PCB isomers in quantities of 0.02 to 0.04 pounds (i.e., 10 to
20 grams) each at its Supelco Park facility in Bellefonte, PA. The petitioner estimates that a 10 to 20 gram production
lot of an individual pure PCB isomer would represent a 3 to 5 year supply. Total annual production is projected at less
